&lt;p&gt;The&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Reports and Assessments Staff Officer III will support the HUMINT &amp;amp; Sensitive Activities Directorate within the Office of the Under Secretary of War for Intelligence and Security (OUSW(I&amp;amp;S)). This role involves preparing and staffing reports, analyzing data, and supporting the coordination of sensitive activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Location:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;nbsp;Pentagon, Arlington, VA&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clearance: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;TS/SCI Clearance&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities and/or Success Factors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Report Preparation and Analysis:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the preparation and staffing of DoW quarterly reports and briefings on sensitive activities for Congress and Executive Branch Senior Leaders. This includes tasks such as collecting, compiling, editing, reviewing, approving, producing, and delivering reports and briefings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Meeting Coordination:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate, convene, and facilitate meetings, working groups, and the Sensitive Activities Executive Council (SA-EXCON) by preparing and disseminating agendas, read-ahead materials, attendee rosters, and meeting minutes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Analysis and Visualization:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and evaluate large data sets, developing data analytics and visualization tools to identify trends, anomalies, and provide data-informed assessments and decision-making support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, update, and maintain data-analytic dashboards using tools like Kibana to interpret historical data, predict future performance, and drive executive-level decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Methodology Development:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify methodologies and statistical methods to find patterns and relationships in large volumes of government-classified structured and unstructured data sets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Support and Collaboration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support government-led production of analysis, assessments, reporting, and briefings for specific activities, enabling data-informed oversight and decision support for senior DoW and Executive Branch officials, and Congressional Staff members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with software capability, security developers, and program managers using Agile and traditional development methodologies to enable and support delivery of data collection, analysis, and reporting objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Strategy and Policy Support:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Suppor

